    "grade": "red",
    "notes": "ELIMINATED - Military Complex\n\nSite is located within a military complex, making it unsuitable for commercial operation.\n\nOriginal tender note: \"Gate permit is required to access this site\"\n\nDecision: Remove from consideration entirely.",
