    "population_data": "ADNOC Service Station Majed (578) is located on Al Ittihad Street (Union Street) in Ajman, near the Al Bustan area. Source: PoloMap (https://ae.polomap.com/ajman/88430). Al Bustan is one of the oldest and most densely populated areas in Ajman, centrally located about 6.4 km from city center, situated beside Ajman Free Zone. Source: Bayut (https://www.bayut.com/area-guides/al-bustan/). Overall Ajman emirate population: ~582,852 (2024). Ajman city: ~565,767 (97% of emirate). Source: Global Media Insight (https://www.globalmediainsight.com/blog/uae-population-statistics/). District-level data not available beyond 2017 census.",
